4:
Lady Elmara, good luck with your
excursion!
7:
Thank you, my fair maiden. Your
kind words shall help me forge
onward.
11:
I swear, on this blade, I will return
from the Kaleidoscope victorious!
18:
She looks like a knight from the
Farlands. Did... she just say she's
headed for the Kaleidoscope?
22:
Wait a moment. Are you the
adventurers the rumors speak of?
26:
Dang, you're a total hottie! Cute to
boot! What's your name—
31:
Er, my apologies. Your beauty
caught me off guard, and I lost my
composure.
36:
C-composure? It was more like you
transformed into a different person...
40:
I must also apologize for not
noticing you earlier. A good knight
should always properly greet a
beautiful maiden.
44:
Uh... I suppose that's not an incorrect
statement.
53:
I am Elmara, knight and royal guard
of a certain princess from a certain
kingdom!
56:
Though at present, I am primarily an
adventurer in search of my country's
lost relics.
57:
You are all adventurers as well, yes?
Famous ones, at that.
60:
I guess? I have a feeling we're
probably famous for all the wrong
reasons...
64:
Lady Stella, are you headed to the
Kaleidoscope? If you are, I would be
honored to serve as your guard.
74:
My thanks! To be accompanied by
such a stunning goddess... Good
fortune smiles upon me this day!
76:
Let us be off, my lady! I shall remain
vigilant by your side!
83: Taste the steel of my blade! Raagh!
90:
Y-yes... Your swordsmanship is very
impressive.
97:
Glad am I to see you unharmed, my
lady. There is no greater joy for a
knight—
102:
Ngh, forget it! I can't hold back
anymore!
108:
Stella, you're just too CUTE! Ohhh,
and your cheeks are so soft and
squishy!
112:
Your cheeks are soft and squishy
too.
116:
I'm guessing this is the real you, and
the stiff knight stuff was the act.
125:
Might as well come completely
clean! I'm Elmara, Mirean knight and
personal guard of the princess first
in line to inherit!
129: So the rest of it was true...
133:
Hey, I take offense to that! No matter
how much I act, I never outright lie! I
meant everything I said about Stella
too!
137:
But it looks like we'll have to put that
conversation on hold...
141:
Not that I'm complaining! I love a
good fight! Leave this to me!
151:
Phew, that was a blast! Nothing like
playing the role to perfection and
keeping a pretty gal safe!
158:
Heheh, thanks! All the effort was
worth it to see you smile!
162:
You both were pretty impressive too,
just like the rumors said!
164:
Couldn't have asked for a more
perfect day!
168:
It was good for us as well. Things
went more smoothly than usual
thanks to your impressive
swordsmanship.
172:
Ehehe, you mean it? Well, I guess I'm
not called Mirea's strongest knight
for nothing!
175:
If you're up for it, want to team up
again sometime? Kaleidoscope
diving is much more fun when you
guys are around!
179:
Are you certain? I thought you would
be focused on finding those relics of
yours.
185:
Our princess suddenly left one day,
saying she was going to look for the
relics!
190: What? This is no laughing matter!
193:
Wait... You said you were from Mirea,
right? So that's how she left home...
198:
Hm? The way you phrased that...
Don't tell me you know Princess Toria?
208: We can take you to her.
213:
Whoooa, what is this place? This is
so cool!
221:
I can't believe you're okay with
letting me in here! You're even more
awesome than I thought!
225:
Um... Just to be clear, you'll have to
keep this a secret from other people.
230:
No worries on that front! I can keep
a secret as safe as a
maiden—especially one this
interesting!
240:
Princess Toria! Hey, how's it going?
I've been looking all over for you!
243:
You know, I'm kind of offended you
found this place before me and
didn't share!
247: No beating around the bush, huh...
251:
We have a lot of fun things here. I
can show them to you.
259:
Phew, all this excitement's got my
heart pounding! I feel so alive!
